Package utils

Class ArrowPatterns

java.lang.Object
utils.ArrowPatterns
public final class ArrowPatterns extends Object
ArrowPatterns is a utility class used to generate various patterns of FieldArrows for a graph object.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Charlie Herbert

    • createRectangularPattern

      public static void createRectangularPattern(Graph2D graph, double density)
      Generates a rectangular pattern of FieldArrows on the graph using the provided density argument.
      Parameters:
      graph - the graph to add the arrows to.
      density - the density of the pattern. Should be less than 1 and must be more than 0.
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if density is less than 0.
